attributionInfo.brokerName: Realty One Group At the Beach Newport
Realty One Group At the Beach Newport

data.description: Welcome to coastal living at its finest! This home invites you into a world where bay views and serene living converge. The home sprawls across 3,213 square feet, featuring three bedrooms, three baths, and a myriad of spaces designed for both relaxation and creativity, including a pair of garages with room for three vehicles approximately over 900 square feet, versatile large shop areas, dedicated pump house for the well, a hot tub, and not one, but two bonus rooms - the first nestled within the home and the second adjacent to the garage, complete with water connections and electrical. A charming outbuilding doubles as a chicken coop, offering a touch of rustic charm. As you step through the door, the home welcomes you with a flood of natural light that dances across an expansive living room, where a cozy wood-burning fireplace awaits to warm your evenings. The residence boasts an effortless open floor plan that elegantly unites the living, dining, and kitchen spaces, crafting the perfect backdrop for unforgettable gatherings and the simple joys of daily life. The kitchen is outfitted with custom butcher block countertops, sleek stainless-steel appliances, and an abundance of cabinets and shelves. Upgraded electrical amenities in the adjacent dining area complement the thoughtful design. Outside, the generous yard beckons you to cultivate your garden, indulge in outdoor pursuits, or bask in the coastal sunshine. Additional perks include an expansive driveway with dedicated RV parking for your adventures. This gem is mere minutes from the historic charm of Newport's Bayfront, where exquisite dining, vibrant arts, boutique shopping, and more await. Schedule your appoint today!
